Not only this high pressure steam cleaner can be used for cleaning away the dirty and stains on the kitchen, bathroom, floor, tile, but also can serve for car detailing. Help you say goodbye to a lot of cleaning tools.

【10s Fast Heating & 1.5L Water Tank】With a 10-second fast heating feature and no waiting required, the steam cleaner for upholstery for car sprays strong pressured steam, unlike other steam cleaners that take 3–4 minutes to heat up and need breaks every 2 minutes to reheat and rebuild pressure; in addition, this steamer for car detailing features a larger water tank with a capacity of 1500ml, allowing for longer cleaning times and less refilling.

【Efficient & Lightweight】Tired of struggling with bulky, heavy cleaning equipment? Our steam cleaners for home use is lightweight and easy to maneuver, making it perfect for tackling hard-to-reach areas like corners, crevices, and tight spaces. Up to 1-hour run time, helping you complete small cleaning tasks in your home. Effortlessly clean your home with our powerful steam cleaner!

【Excellent Service】We are so confident in AUXCO steam cleaner quality. We provide you 2 Years-Warranty with satisfactory after-sales service. If you have any questions, please contact us, and we will solve it within 24hrs (No Need to Return Product). We're always here.
【Kind Reminder】 To avoid getting burned, please wear gloves and ensure that the upholstery steam cleaner is properly installed to avoid air and water leaks .
